PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1496 and 1510 - SCHEDULE F) by making provision for the sale of non-prescription medications for the treatment of heartburn if they contain no more than 20 mg of FAMOTIDINE or 150 mg of RANITIDINE per oral dosage unit.
